Welcome to DayJot, the simple, permanent journaling app.

How's your day going? To get started, simply reply to this email with your first entry.

A few notes:

- Only you can read what you write, so there is no wrong way to do this.
- You can reply to this email as many times as you like. Subsequent responses will be appended to your entry.  
- You can format your entry with Markdown, a simple markup syntax.

If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to shoot an email to help@dayjot.com. 